title: Game Theory & Money Week 2
itunes:title: Game Theory & Money Week 2
description:
In the Week 2 edition of Game Theory and Money, Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith talked about Week 1 quarterback performances, Cynthia asked her surprise question for Money and their game picks were announced during the "Frelund Four-cast" and "10 games in 10 minutes" segments. Cynthia also explained which teams will score the most in "Points on Points" and which teams she trusted the most in "Confidence Index."

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
